{"tid":885303,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"短而密的分隔線是什麼意思？","createTime":"2018-11-01T08:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T07:48:20.000Z","uid":66242,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ebee727046b350705bdbf25f975391730726eb46","tid":885303,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qkJ9GAv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqkJ9GAv.png&h=e0ba328a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右邊的是危險警告線<br />\n通常在高速公路分岔出口<br />\n有左邊這種短而密的點點線<br />\n感覺上這些位置應該相當危險<br />\n理論上應該盡早選定行車線<br />\n避免在分岔口轉線<br />\n但根據運輸署定義就沒有指明其意思<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmnKvs1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmnKvs1.png&h=94ec549c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n究竟是怎樣？"},{"pid":"389b461e220ffc27d141f498916866155de10f1f","tid":885303,"uid":13919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"提示最左線即將會有支路出口 通常見到會cut定入去"},{"pid":"f240fca44f6a96cffe1a82f8c369e404e3bfa02b","tid":885303,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":38,"score":-38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"你張圖好似唔係香港既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487ca19e53033379e216f62716adb66828dd7c2b","tid":885303,"uid":142351,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:09:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e261def9efaaf205181fa64ca24558de200d3ae","tid":885303,"uid":145496,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"487ca19e53033379e216f62716adb66828dd7c2b","tid":885303,"uid":142351,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"f240fca44f6a96cffe1a82f8c369e404e3bfa02b","tid":885303,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":38,"score":-38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"你張圖好似唔係香港既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:09:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":